import { Button, Paper, Typography } from "@mui/material"
import { Box } from "@mui/system"

export const SolicitarGrt = ({ loginUser }) => {

    const valor = 1.50


    return (
        <>
            <Typography variant='h6' color='primary'> Solicitar GRT</Typography>

            <Box sx={{ width: '100%' }}>
                <Paper sx={{ p: 4, m: 2 }} elevation={6} >
                    <Typography>Valor por GRT: R$ {valor.toFixed(2)} </Typography>
                </Paper>
            </Box>
            <Button>Solicitar</Button>
        </>
    )
}
